<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5> blow off steam • blow smoke</xh5><p> <i>blow off steam</i>—(also: let off steam) give vent to one’s anger or frustration (by talking in an unrestrained manner, etc.): Perhaps the best way to <u>blow off steam</u> and get rid of stress is through exercise.</p><p> <i>blow smoke—</i>speak deceptively; brag or exaggerate: Hopefully they aren’t <u>blowing smoke</u> about how good they are because I’ve invested heavily with them.</p> </entry>
